    "updated_at": "2023-04-02T14:53:38Z",
    "body": "To elaborate, the issue is that Terminal.app does not support true color (`#9A348E`). The named colors (`yellow`) and short color codes (`3`) should work. The one thing starship could do is use a close simple color instead if the terminal does not support truecolor.",
