    "created_at": "2023-04-02T14:59:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-04-02T14:59:58Z",
    "body": "One workaround for now is to define two `palettes`, use the defined color names, and switch between a true color and regular palette via `starship config palette palette_name` on shell startup based on the value of `$TERM_PROGRAM`.",
